sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI/SDK)
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as model-registry proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as model-registry controller<br/>8081/TCP (health)
    participant KServePod as KServe Inference Pod
    participant CSI as CSI Storage Initializer
    participant AsyncJob as async-upload Job<br/>(Python)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API

    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3
    IstioGW->>Proxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP (Istio mTLS in-mesh)<br/>AuthorizationPolicy enforced
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT registered model<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>Proxy: Success
    Proxy-->>IstioGW: 201 Created (JSON)
    IstioGW-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 2: InferenceService Synchronization

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CRDs<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Proxy: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/inference_services<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT inference_service metadata
    DB-->>Proxy: Success
    Proxy-->>Controller: 201 Created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update labels/finalizers<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over KServePod,Proxy: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI

    KServePod->>CSI: Init container starts<br/>storageUri: model-registry://model/v1
    CSI->>Proxy: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/model_artifacts<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: None
    Proxy->>DB: SELECT artifact metadata
    DB-->>Proxy: Artifact location (S3 URI)
    Proxy-->>CSI: Artifact metadata (JSON)
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifact<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
    S3-->>CSI: Model files
    CSI-->>KServePod: Model ready at /mnt/models

    Note over AsyncJob,Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload

    AsyncJob->>S3: Download source model<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>AsyncJob: Model artifacts
    AsyncJob->>OCI: Upload as OCI image (skopeo)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Docker credentials
    OCI-->>AsyncJob: Push success
    AsyncJob->>Sigstore: Sign artifact (cosign)<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: OIDC Token
    Sigstore-->>AsyncJob: Signature
    AsyncJob->>Proxy: Register model/version/artifact<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8080/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT model metadata
    DB-->>Proxy: Success
    Proxy-->>AsyncJob: 201 Created
